  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate the weight-sparing effect of detemir and assess
      glycemic control and treatment satisfaction when switching from NPH to detemir, to improve
      metabolic control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
